* feat(design-system): budget display, viral fission system & welcome page polish

- Add useBudget hook with weekly $20 base, 5h $10 window, and independent bonus pool (Star +$3, Share +$2) with 7-day expiry
- Sidebar budget indicator with progress bar, click-to-expand detail panel showing weekly/window/bonus usage
- Low-budget warning banner (< 20%) with dismiss button, only shown when using nexu official models
- Depleted state full-screen overlay with BYOK guidance and viral entry points
- Merged GitHub Star + viral card on Home page with reward badges
- Welcome page copy refresh: title/subtitle rewrite, logo upgrade, BYOK text link
- AuthShell footer: © 2026 Powerformer, Inc. + Terms/Privacy links moved from AuthPage
- 44 new locale strings (EN + ZH) for budget, viral, and tooltip copy
- AGENTS.md memory updates from continual-learning

Made-with: Cursor

* research(competitive): add OpenClaw ecosystem full competitive analysis

- 14 个竞品深度分析报告（ArkClaw、Clawion、ClawX、Copaw、KimiClaw、MaxClaw 等）
- 12 个竞品简报（brief 格式，含场景、增长、定价）
- OpenClaw 生态全量列表（含飞书导出 CSV/MD）
- 3 份研究报告（开源增长、飞书生态、生态全景）
- 7 条战略洞察（clone/memory/ideas）
- 竞品调研框架文档
- 更新 competitive-analysis.md 主文档

Made-with: Cursor

* feat(settings): add General tab with account, language, behavior, privacy, and updates sections

- Add two-tab layout (General / AI Model Providers) to SettingsView
- General tab includes: Account (signed-in/signed-out states with avatar initials), Language (Select dropdown with native + English labels), Application Behavior (launch at login + show in Dock), Data & Privacy (usage analytics + crash reports), Updates (version + check now), About
- Remove settings item from main nav — accessible only via bottom-left footer button
- Add sidebar footer single-row layout: settings button (flex-1) + help (?) + GitHub icons
- Language switcher upgraded from segmented control to Radix Select with two-line items
- i18n: add all new keys in both en and zh (ws.settings.tab.*, ws.settings.account.*, ws.settings.behavior.*, ws.settings.data.*, ws.settings.updates.*, ws.settings.about.*)
- Update settings subtitle to reflect broader scope
- Remove budget warning banners (warning + depleted) from Home dashboard

Made-with: Cursor

* fix(settings): update launch-at-login copy — 开机时启动应用 / Launch at startup

- zh: 登录时启动应用 → 开机时启动应用
- zh desc: 当您的计算机启动时，自动打开 nexu → 当您的电脑开机启动时自动打开 Nexu
- en: Launch at login → Launch at startup
- en desc: Automatically open nexu → Automatically open Nexu when your computer starts

Made-with: Cursor

* fix: remove unused FolderOpen import and local folder constants after merge

Made-with: Cursor
