From a93109f18c1179cb59482807a12cf696b668f722 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: chaoxiaoche <fanzhen910412@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 31 Mar 2026 19:49:56 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 6/9] =?UTF-8?q?design-system:=20=E7=94=A8=E9=87=8F?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E4=B8=8E=E5=A5=96=E5=8A=B1=E4=BB=BB=E5=8A=A1=E4=BE=A7=E6=A0=8F?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E4=BA=A4=E4=BA=92=E4=B8=8E=20UI=20(#111)?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

* design-system: rewards, usage budget, and sidebar task UI

- Rewards Center: task rows, CTAs, fixed 150px pills, daily/weekly states,
  material modal flow, confirm modals, locale strings
- Sidebar: budget strip hover (accent-subtle), rewards teaser without
  inner icon frame or task count, full title copy
- Channel icons: Xiaohongshu (Simple Icons wordmark), Feishu PNG, Jike SVG
- Links: reward rules use ArrowUpRight; social frequency 12px
- index.css: Design Spec updates for rewards, sidebar teaser, budget strip
- Toaster (App), budget hooks, ChannelDetail tweaks, data alignment

Made-with: Cursor

* design-system: rewards and sidebar UI polish after PR #111

- Earn more: full credit(s) copy, task title/reward gap, CTA size and ghost style
- Rewards list: section spacing, countdown-to-CTA gap, no layout FLIP animation
- Home: remove official usage card; sidebar Earn more teaser without shadow
- Material modal: steps heading, 14px steps, fixed-height column with bottom CTA
- Locale and index.css Design Specs aligned with implementation

Made-with: Cursor

* design-system: reward CTAs 8px radius, compact height; Jike mark SVG

Align task-row and material-modal primary buttons with global action
button tokens (rounded-[8px], min-h-9). Replace Jike asset with official
mark. Channel detail: link icon after text, column gap for bubbles.
Update Rewards design specs in index.css.

Made-with: Cursor

* refactor(design-system): extract UI components + convert CSS to @utility — net -995 lines (#115)

Phase 1: Modularize index.css
- Split landing animations → animations-landing.css (61 lines)
- Split markdown styles → markdown.css (31 lines)
- Convert 13 CSS classes to Tailwind 4 @utility directives
- Condense Design Spec comments from 700+ to ~80 lines
- index.css reduced from 1538 → 668 lines

Phase 2: Extract 5 React components
- FilterPills — pill/segment toggle (variant, emoji, count support)
- UnderlineTabs — underline tab bar (sm/md, icon, badge)
- PageHeader — title + description + actions slot (sm/md/lg spacing)
- StatusDot — semantic status indicator (8 statuses, 4 sizes)
- NavItem — sidebar nav link (default/compact density)

Replacements across 20 files:
- 6× PageHeader (OpenClawWorkspace, BillingPage, DashboardPage)
- 6× FilterPills (segment + pill variants)
- 8× UnderlineTabs (SkillsPage, CloneBuilderPage, TeamPage, etc.)
- 16× StatusDot (online/idle/busy/away across 11 files)
- 2× NavItem (primary nav + conversations)

Updated code-style.mdc Layer 1+2 tables with new components.
JS bundle: 1,902 → 1,899 KB. Build passes with zero errors.

Made-with: Cursor

Co-authored-by: chaoxiaoche <chaoxiaoche@chaoxiaochedeMacBook-Pro.local>

---------

Co-authored-by: chaoxiaoche <chaoxiaoche@chaoxiaochedeMacBook-Pro.local>
