-       rounded-full bg-success/10 text-success text-[10px]/500 leading-none
-       Dot: w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-success shrink-0
-     - Model selector: inline in status line, click to open dropdown
-     - CTA: "Chat in [Platform]" — bg-accent rounded-xl px-4 py-2
-       - Dynamic: switches text/icon based on activeChannelId
-       - Flip animation: scale-y-0/opacity-0 → scale-y-100/opacity-100, 300ms
