-   ── Inline Model Selector (Hero status line) ──
-   - Trigger: click on model name in status bar (11px text-text-muted)
-   - Shows provider logo (11px) + model name + ChevronDown (9px)
-   - Dropdown: absolute z-50, w-[280px], rounded-xl, bg-surface-1, shadow-xl
-   - Search: bg-surface-0, border, 12px text, autoFocus
