-/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-   Desktop Client Layout — Design Rule (implement with Tailwind)
-   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-
-   RULE: nexu is a desktop client. The layout is ALWAYS horizontal
-   (sidebar left + content right). Never use responsive breakpoints
-   that collapse sidebar below content.
