-   └────────┴──────────────────────────────────┘
-
-   - Root container: flex flex-row h-full (NEVER flex-col or lg:flex-row)
-   - Sidebar: shrink-0, dynamic width via state (default 192px), bg transparent
-   - Main: flex-1 overflow-hidden min-h-0 bg-surface-1 rounded-l-[12px] pt-8
-     Left rounded corners (12px) create refined panel-over-sidebar effect
-     pt-8 (32px) top padding clears traffic light zone for all views
-   - Page inner padding: pt-2 pb-6 sm:pb-8 (Skills, Settings)
-     Reduced top padding to compensate for main pt-8
-   - Mobile header: hidden (desktop client has no mobile state)
-
