-
-   Three-state system controlled by hasUpdate + updateDismissed:
-   - hasUpdate=true, updateDismissed=false → Bottom banner visible
-   - hasUpdate=true, updateDismissed=true  → Logo badge visible
-   - hasUpdate=false                       → Both hidden (installed / no update)
-
