-   - Header row: flex items-center justify-between mb-1.5
-     - Left: green pulse dot (h-2 w-2, animate-ping) + text
-     - Right: X button (dismiss) or progress % (10px tabular-nums text-muted)
-   - Text: 12px/500 text-primary, whitespace-nowrap
-     - Available: "v0.2.0 available"
-     - Downloading: "Downloading…"
-     - Ready: "v0.2.0 ready"
-     - Error: "Update failed" (dot turns red)
-   - Progress row (downloading only):
