"升级 Pro · 11,000 积分/月" with a conversion hint (5.5x capacity uplift),
followed by credit packs as a secondary option. This improves the upsell
funnel at the highest-intent moment.

Also includes: UsagePage, CapabilitiesPanel, pricing page refinements,
plugin/connector data, and related knowledge updates from the billing UX
iteration.

