  secondary = credit packs, tertiary = BYOK
- Pro users: primary = credit packs, secondary = BYOK
- Free users: primary = BYOK + "升级套餐" (accent color)

This improves the upsell funnel by surfacing the Pro upgrade at the
highest-intent moment (when credits are running low).

